my-claw/sdp/prd-glyphweave-studio-loop.md:52:| GSL-009 | Add lightweight cost/time accounting for art sessions: render duration, model time, total wall time, and optional per-session cost estimate where provider pricing exists. | SHOULD | T2 | - Session summary includes wall time + model time<br/>- Costs recorded when pricing info exists<br/>- Last session summary can be shown without scanning logs |
