  sdp fractal init <prd.md>     Generate depth-0 skeleton from PRD
  sdp fractal scan [path]       Analyze modules and report current depth
  sdp fractal deepen [--target] Generate tasks for next depth, load into queue
  sdp fractal status            Show resolution map across the project
"""

